systemctl status httpd


Here i got error nginx  failed
Because both servers are listening on same port 80
So i configured nginx port number 80 to 8080
#vi /etc/nginx/nginx.defualt
Listen port number 8080
save&exit
Restart the nginx
Then check 
systemctl start nginx
systemctl status nginx
We can check ports 
By using
#netstat -tulpn | grep LISTEN




